1
00:00:00,799 --> 00:00:05,750
I asked some of the boys, “What is your
policy?”

2
00:00:05,750 --> 00:00:08,200
They said, “We have no policy."

3
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:10,530
“Then what is your aim?”

4
00:00:10,530 --> 00:00:12,130
“We have no aim."

5
00:00:12,130 --> 00:00:14,260
“Then why are you doing this nonsense?”

6
00:00:14,260 --> 00:00:18,589
They said, “Because whatever the elders
tell us, we do it."

7
00:00:18,589 --> 00:00:21,519
I said, “Have you no personality?

8
00:00:21,519 --> 00:00:22,519
Nothing?”

9
00:00:22,519 --> 00:00:29,960
Is exactly what happened when this hippy movement
started.

10
00:00:29,960 --> 00:00:36,280
Some so-called intellectuals started this
horrible hippy movement in the West.

11
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:42,720
And when they found they cannot do anything
about it, they found it’s going to fail,

12
00:00:42,720 --> 00:00:50,090
so many children lost their education, so
many children I know became pregnant, girls

13
00:00:50,090 --> 00:00:56,070
and boys [sadist scout/squat].

14
00:00:56,070 --> 00:01:01,340
All that took them to the extreme that they
became violent.

15
00:01:01,340 --> 00:01:08,700
But unless and until there is a change within
yourself, how can we change anything outside?

16
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:10,660
We cannot.

17
00:01:10,660 --> 00:01:16,910
And the first seven people I fought were all
hippies.

18
00:01:16,910 --> 00:01:18,750
Very difficult.

19
00:01:18,750 --> 00:01:25,340
They called themselves hippies but they used
to hog like a pig.

20
00:01:25,340 --> 00:01:33,500
They wanted all the comforts, everything free,
extremely dominating and quarrelsome people.

21
00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:37,090
But the foundation was laid on them.

22
00:01:37,090 --> 00:01:38,270
Very surprising.

23
00:01:38,270 --> 00:01:45,050
But I had to work on them for at least four
years regularly.

24
00:01:45,050 --> 00:01:56,650
So that is how Sahaja Yoga started, and today
you know how much it has spread, how far it

25
00:01:56,650 --> 00:01:57,780
has gone.

26
00:01:57,780 --> 00:02:02,740
Only in Maharashtra this problem is there
of so-called intellectuals, this is called

27
00:02:02,740 --> 00:02:05,990
themselves, but they have no intelligence.

28
00:02:05,990 --> 00:02:08,700
I talked to one man; I got fed up.

29
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:11,090
He didn’t know anything about spirituality,
he didn’t know anything about medicine,

30
00:02:11,090 --> 00:02:12,620
he didn’t know anything about science.

31
00:02:12,620 --> 00:02:17,800
I said, “Now, what do you know?”

32
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:20,760
So it was impossible.

33
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:26,615
So such people who are jobless ? we call them
[nikaam bekaar] ? they have no work, they

34
00:02:26,615 --> 00:02:31,520
are starting all such things and we should
not be upset with them.

35
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:37,600
They are trying to create problems and they
are getting money from some sources.

36
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:45,840
They are afraid, I think the politicians are
afraid, perhaps, that Sahaja Yoga may turn

37
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:54,390
their tables down because we believe in honesty,
and maybe a day may come when these honest

38
00:02:54,390 --> 00:02:56,240
people might harm them, perhaps.

39
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:58,460
I do not know why.

40
00:02:58,460 --> 00:03:05,350
This may be one of the reasons these people
are frightened of us.

41
00:03:05,350 --> 00:03:16,650
Or whatever it is we have to understand that
for doing any great work one has to sacrifice.

42
00:03:16,650 --> 00:03:22,290
Of course, you are not going to be crucified
like Christ, no.

43
00:03:22,290 --> 00:03:27,500
Nor you have to sacrifice as my parents sacrificed
for the independence of this country.

44
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:30,349
Nor you are going to be tortured.

45
00:03:30,349 --> 00:03:34,350
But really, inconveniences you may have.

46
00:03:34,350 --> 00:03:40,620
But I must thank you very much because of
you are coming here and singing Marathi songs.

47
00:03:40,620 --> 00:03:46,080
They are quite impressed and they think it’s
only possible because you are all Sahaja yogis.

48
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:51,180
Otherwise you could not have done.

49
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:59,250
So if there are any inconveniences think that
it’s a joke; that’s all.

50
00:03:59,250 --> 00:04:06,690
Today I was thinking we should do the Puja
of Shri chakra and Lalita chakra which we

51
00:04:06,690 --> 00:04:07,740
have never done.

52
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:16,769
This is the right place to do these two chakras
today.

53
00:04:16,769 --> 00:04:26,449
Lot has been written about Shri chakra and
about Lalita chakra, but to understand fundamentally

54
00:04:26,449 --> 00:04:40,129
the left side when it reaches up to Vishuddhi,
then it uses on the right side the Shri chakra,

55
00:04:40,129 --> 00:04:48,659
on the left side the Lalita chakra, to manifest
itself.

56
00:04:48,659 --> 00:05:01,559
These two chakras are the ones who manifest
all that you see.

57
00:05:01,559 --> 00:05:15,210
But these chakras are the ones who emit vibrations
of different kinds, and because of their angularities,

58
00:05:15,210 --> 00:05:21,919
like if you have some sort of a cardboard
attached with small, small holes of different

59
00:05:21,919 --> 00:05:27,349
colors and which rotates all the time, you
get different colors.

60
00:05:27,349 --> 00:05:31,479
Also you can get different permutations and
combinations.

61
00:05:31,479 --> 00:05:40,650
In the same way, different permutations and
combinations are created, and that is how

62
00:05:40,650 --> 00:05:44,979
you get all the advantages of Sahaja Yoga.

63
00:05:44,979 --> 00:05:48,029
So these two chakras are very important.

64
00:05:48,029 --> 00:05:56,110
I do not know if you know of any mantras about
Shri chakra but I’ll give you a book, later

65
00:05:56,110 --> 00:06:01,229
on I’ll translate it to you and you can
compose something for Shri chakra.

66
00:06:01,229 --> 00:06:08,869
Shri chakra on the right side, Lalita chakra
on the left side, so what we are really worshipping

67
00:06:08,869 --> 00:06:15,960
today is Mahasaraswati power and Mahakali
power, both put together.

68
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:20,309
So now we started combining things, not individual.

69
00:06:20,309 --> 00:06:26,210
Now, these two energies are very important.

70
00:06:26,210 --> 00:06:31,129
Without the energy, without the power, nothing
exists.

71
00:06:31,129 --> 00:06:43,710
For example, if this light had no power to
give light or to burn, it is useless.

72
00:06:43,710 --> 00:06:53,220
In the same way, without getting your realization
you are useless because your power is not

73
00:06:53,220 --> 00:06:56,499
awakened, at least not complete.

74
00:06:56,499 --> 00:07:13,389
But these two powers give us lots of benefits
even without realization.

75
00:07:13,389 --> 00:07:23,240
Whatever you see in this world created is
done by these two chakras of the Adi Shakti.

76
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:26,150
But here the power doesn’t move.

77
00:07:26,150 --> 00:07:28,910
It’s not moving.

78
00:07:28,910 --> 00:07:34,439
But in the human being the power start moving.

79
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:47,969
And when it starts moving, then we can say
it is creating another world.

80
00:07:47,969 --> 00:07:51,889
But movement is not the only thing.

81
00:07:51,889 --> 00:08:00,530
This power acts, gives you intelligence, gives
you all kinds of things which you have as

82
00:08:00,530 --> 00:08:03,499
human beings.

83
00:08:03,499 --> 00:08:11,869
But later on this power itself becomes enlightened
within you when the left and right side both

84
00:08:11,869 --> 00:08:14,389
become enlightened.

85
00:08:14,389 --> 00:08:23,899
This enlightenment, you get it when you get
your Self-realization, but not immediately,

86
00:08:23,899 --> 00:08:24,899
not immediately.

87
00:08:24,899 --> 00:08:27,490
This, one should understand.

88
00:08:27,490 --> 00:08:39,000
For example, if you have pain or if your chakra
is catching, you have to use your hands.

89
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,860
You cannot say that, “The energy is flowing
within me.

90
00:08:40,860 --> 00:08:41,860
So it’s all right.

91
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:43,050
I can manage."

92
00:08:43,050 --> 00:08:45,870
It’s not like that.

93
00:08:45,870 --> 00:08:54,410
You have to use your hands to impart that
power to yourself or to others.

94
00:08:54,410 --> 00:09:00,470
If you have pain in the stomach then you can
say that, “If there’s energy in my stomach

95
00:09:00,470 --> 00:09:04,610
why should I have pain in the stomach?”

96
00:09:04,610 --> 00:09:09,750
But the play of these chakras have to come.

97
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:20,920
And that is why you have to use your power
of your hands.

98
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:31,300
If you cannot use your hands then you cannot
impart this energy.

99
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:39,769
Many people have asked Me that, “Mother,
when will it move horizontal?”

100
00:09:39,769 --> 00:09:43,209
It will move horizontal, no doubt.

101
00:09:43,209 --> 00:09:44,920
It does.

102
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:54,790
But even that horizontal movement is to be
guided by these two very important chakras.

103
00:09:54,790 --> 00:09:58,990
So you must understand the importance of these
two chakras within yourself.

104
00:09:58,990 --> 00:10:04,819
That’s why I have told many a times, “Don’t
move your head too many times."

105
00:10:04,819 --> 00:10:11,430
And this way many people talk, I mean, it’s
style of talking, “No, this, that,” very

106
00:10:11,430 --> 00:10:13,800
common with French, specially.

107
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:18,100
That’s another way you are not respecting
your chakras.

108
00:10:18,100 --> 00:10:22,740
Shouldn’t move your shoulders too much.

109
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:25,500
Mostly they talk like this.

110
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:29,430
It’s anti-chakras, anti-chakras.

111
00:10:29,430 --> 00:10:33,000
Should keep your shoulders straight.

112
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:42,230
When you are singing you can move your whole
upper part ? it’s all right ? but not your

113
00:10:42,230 --> 00:10:43,230
shoulders.

114
00:10:43,230 --> 00:10:53,310
This is the thing one has to understand that
these two centers are to be looked after.

115
00:10:53,310 --> 00:10:56,500
You can move your neck, your body, when you
are singing.

116
00:10:56,500 --> 00:11:05,589
It’s important, that helps, but not your
shoulders.

117
00:11:05,589 --> 00:11:07,600
Shoulders are to be kept intact.

118
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:12,990
But while saying just, “Yes,” you need
not go on, “Yes, yes, yes, yes."

119
00:11:12,990 --> 00:11:18,940
It’s a very, very simple thing that it can
have a very bad effect.

120
00:11:18,940 --> 00:11:26,329
And those who move their shoulders too much
do not feel vibrations much because the chakras

121
00:11:26,329 --> 00:11:31,160
are not all right.

122
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:38,190
It’s a very simple thing to be understood
that they are the most important chakras we

123
00:11:38,190 --> 00:11:46,720
have, and whatever is to be used out of this
Paramachaitanya they have to be used by these

124
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:50,269
two centers.

125
00:11:50,269 --> 00:11:55,480
Even supposing your some chakra is catching
on your spinal chord, you have to use your

126
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:59,260
hands.

127
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:02,580
Somebody can say, “I can just put my attention."

128
00:12:02,580 --> 00:12:06,149
Doesn’t work out that good.

129
00:12:06,149 --> 00:12:12,279
Because yet your attention has not that reached
that stage where these chakras, like Lalita

130
00:12:12,279 --> 00:12:16,550
chakra and Shri chakra, obey your attention.

131
00:12:16,550 --> 00:12:22,439
They do not.

132
00:12:22,439 --> 00:12:25,930
So you have to work out with your hands.

133
00:12:25,930 --> 00:12:29,180
Be careful: don’t move your shoulders too
much.

134
00:12:29,180 --> 00:12:36,029
And if you see now Indians when they sing
bhajans they’ll move their whole body, they’ll

135
00:12:36,029 --> 00:12:38,670
do like this, but never their shoulders.

136
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:44,250
The shoulders will move in the same way as
the neck is moving.

137
00:12:44,250 --> 00:12:51,120
They might move their neck also but they’ll
never move their shoulders like this, and

138
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:55,889
it’s regarded as inauspicious according
to Indian standards.

139
00:12:55,889 --> 00:13:03,459
Because of this culture based on what the
saints have told and also about many seers

140
00:13:03,459 --> 00:13:11,480
have told, it is more related to spiritual
life than to materialistic life.

141
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:16,649
Now the materialistic life, unless and until
there is the foundation of the spiritual life,

142
00:13:16,649 --> 00:13:24,060
takes you to a very partial development, you
can say.

143
00:13:24,060 --> 00:13:33,569
But to get a full development you must have
your foundation on spirituality.

144
00:13:33,569 --> 00:13:42,110
That’s why spirituality being the foundation
has to be deep, has to be fully equipped,

145
00:13:42,110 --> 00:13:45,110
has to be absolutely perfect.

146
00:13:45,110 --> 00:13:48,949
Then the whole building can be built.

147
00:13:48,949 --> 00:13:52,740
It’s gone wrong in the West; doesn’t matter.

148
00:13:52,740 --> 00:14:03,360
Now you can build it up and then you’ll
be surprised how you become really solid people.

149
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:08,629
This is a very short talk about Shri chakra.

150
00:14:08,629 --> 00:14:14,779
I think I should sit down and write all about
it and it would be nice handing it for you

151
00:14:14,779 --> 00:14:17,879
