155
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:48,560
But once you can get out of your thoughts
and go into thoughtless awareness, then these

156
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:53,269
chakras start working it out and you start
moving much deeper into your own being.

157
00:14:53,269 --> 00:14:55,220
