inaudible after some time]

158
00:14:55,220 --> 00:14:59,560
I must say that this beautiful Earth has created
so many beautiful things.

159
00:14:59,560 --> 00:15:07,320
But She Herself is nothing but detached, simple
Mother Earth.

160
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:11,470
