161
00:15:11,470 --> 00:15:17,779
When it comes to creation I can create beautiful
things.

162
00:15:17,779 --> 00:15:21,950
You are so beautiful, too, creatures.

163
00:15:21,950 --> 00:15:30,589
But as far as I am concerned I do not think
that I require any one of these things or

164
00:15:30,589 --> 00:15:36,800
I’m bothered about them, or need them or
tempted by them.

165
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:41,800
So what Grégoire has said is because they
are insisting that they are going to give

166
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:46,449
Me presents every year and that’s why this
is a delude to them.

167
00:15:46,449 --> 00:15:49,170
But I’ve been telling them that there’s
no need now.

168
00:15:49,170 --> 00:15:54,529
Let’s say, you all consider it, is only
no need to give so many presents.

169
00:15:54,529 --> 00:15:59,740
